sentences: Slim The Mobster grew up all over from Loudonville, NY to Corpus Christi, Texas.
In February 2008, he was featured on a Hussein Fatal mixtape.
He delivered demos to Dr. Dre in 2008 and eventually got a record deal with Aftermath Entertainment.
=== 2009-2010: Working on Dr. Dre's Detox and debut album ===
Slim The Mobster started to work on Dr. Dre's Detox in 2009, including the single, "Kush".
